<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN" data-theme="light">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>农村自建房风险清单构建 - 智能风险研判</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
<style>
:root {
    --primary: #1a73e8;
    --primary-dark: #1557b0;
    --primary-light: #e8f0fe;
    --secondary: #0097a7;
    --danger: #d93025;
    --warning: #e37400;
    --success: #1e8e3e;
    --bg-dark: #f0f2f5;
    --bg-card: #ffffff;
    --bg-hover: #e8eaed;
    --text-primary: #202124;
    --text-secondary: #5f6368;
    --border: #dadce0;
    --shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    --input-bg: #ffffff;
    --input-border: #dadce0;
    --modal-bg: #ffffff;
    --tag-bg: #f1f3f4;
    --tag-border: #dadce0;
    --header-bg: rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
    --tree-group-bg: rgba(26,115,232,0.06);
    --tree-row-hover: rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
    --dot-red: #d93025;
    --dot-orange: #e37400;
    --dot-yellow: #f9ab00;
    --dot-blue: #1a73e8;
}
:root[data-theme="dark"] {
    --primary: #1e6fdb;
    --primary-dark: #1557b0;
    --primary-light: #e8f1fd;
    --secondary: #00b4d8;
    --danger: #ef4444;
    --warning: #f59e0b;
    --success: #10b981;
    --bg-dark: #0a1628;
    --bg-card: #112240;
    --bg-hover: #1a2f4a;
    --text-primary: #e2e8f0;
    --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
    --border: #1e3a5f;
    --shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    --input-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    --input-border: #1e3a5f;
    --modal-bg: #112240;
    --tag-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    --tag-border: #1e3a5f;
    --header-bg: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    --tree-group-bg: rgba(26,115,232,0.1);
    --tree-row-hover: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    --dot-red: #ef4444;
    --dot-orange: #f59e0b;
    --dot-yellow: #eab308;
    --dot-blue: #3b82f6;
}
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body { font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'PingFang SC', sans-serif; background: var(--bg-dark); color: var(--text-primary); margin: 0; padding: 20px; }

/* Breadcrumb */
.breadcrumb { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 16px; }

/* Card */
.card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 16px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px var(--shadow); }
.card-header { padding: 16px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
.card-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.card-body { padding: 20px; }

/* Filter Bar */
.filter-bar { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
.filter-input { background: var(--input-bg); border: 1px solid var(--input-border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 13px; }
.filter-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); }
.filter-select { background: var(--input-bg); border: 1px solid var(--input-border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 13px; }
.filter-select:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); }

/* Buttons */
.btn { padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; border: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); }
.btn-outline { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-secondary); }
.btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary); }

/* Risk dot */
.risk-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; }
.risk-dot.red { background: var(--dot-red); }
.risk-dot.orange { background: var(--dot-orange); }
.risk-dot.yellow { background: var(--dot-yellow); }
.risk-dot.blue { background: var(--dot-blue); }

/* Risk tag */
.risk-tag { padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
.risk-tag.red { background: rgba(217,48,37,0.12); color: var(--dot-red); }
.risk-tag.orange { background: rgba(227,116,0,0.12); color: var(--dot-orange); }
.risk-tag.yellow { background: rgba(249,171,0,0.12); color: var(--dot-yellow); }
.risk-tag.blue { background: rgba(26,115,232,0.12); color: var(--dot-blue); }

/* Tree table */
.tree-table-header { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 90px 1fr 70px 120px; gap: 0; padding: 10px 16px; background: var(--header-bg); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); }
.tree-group-header { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 16px; background: var(--tree-group-bg); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary); font-size: 13px; user-select: none; transition: background .15s; }
.tree-group-header:hover { background: rgba(26,115,232,0.15); }
.tree-group-header .toggle-arrow { margin-right: 6px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); transition: transform .2s; display: inline-block; }
.tree-group-header.collapsed .toggle-arrow { transform: rotate(-90deg); }
.tree-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 90px 1fr 70px 120px; gap: 0; padding: 8px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px; align-items: center; transition: background .15s; }
.tree-row:hover { background: var(--tree-row-hover); }
.tree-row .cell-content { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
.tree-row .cell-actions a { margin-right: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 12px; color: var(--primary); cursor: pointer; }
.tree-row .cell-actions a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
.tree-row .cell-actions a.del { color: var(--danger); }
.tree-row .cell-actions a.del:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
.tree-stats { display: flex; gap: 16px; padding: 10px 16px; background: var(--header-bg); font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px; }
.tree-stats span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }

/* Modal */
.modal-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); z-index: 9999; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start; padding-top: 30px; overflow-y: auto; }
.modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
.modal-box { background: var(--modal-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; width: 92%; max-width: 1100px; box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; max-height: 92vh; }
.modal-box .modal-header { padding: 16px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
.modal-box .modal-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.modal-box .modal-close { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; border: none; background: var(--bg-hover); cursor: pointer; font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all .2s; }
.modal-box .modal-close:hover { background: var(--danger); color: #fff; }
.modal-box .modal-body { padding: 24px; flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; }
.modal-box .modal-footer { padding: 12px 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: flex-end; flex-shrink: 0; }

/* Form */
.form-row-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.form-row-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 100px; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.form-group { margin-bottom: 0; }
.form-label { display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.form-label .required { color: var(--danger); margin-left: 2px; }
.form-control { width: 100%; background: var(--input-bg); border: 1px solid var(--input-border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; }
.form-control:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26,115,232,0.1); }
.form-control[readonly] { opacity: 0.6; cursor: not-allowed; }
textarea.form-control { resize: vertical; }

/* Combo tree dropdown */
.combo-wrap { position: relative; }
.combo-wrap input { width: 100%; padding-right: 32px; }
.combo-arrow { position: absolute; right: 10px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: var(--text-secondary); cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; }
.combo-tree-dropdown { position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; top: 100%; margin-top: 2px; background: var(--modal-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); z-index: 100; max-height: 260px; overflow-y: auto; display: none; }
.combo-tree-dropdown.show { display: block; }
.combo-tree-dropdown .ct-node { padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; color: var(--text-primary); }
.combo-tree-dropdown .ct-node:hover { background: rgba(26,115,232,0.08); }
.combo-tree-dropdown .ct-arrow { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-secondary); width: 14px; text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0; cursor: pointer; }
.combo-tree-dropdown .ct-label { flex: 1; }
.combo-tree-dropdown .ct-children { padding-left: 20px; }
.combo-tree-dropdown .ct-children.hidden { display: none; }

/* Rich text editor */
.rte-toolbar { display: flex; gap: 2px; padding: 6px 8px; background: var(--bg-hover); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: none; border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
.rte-toolbar .sep { width: 1px; height: 20px; background: var(--border); margin: 0 4px; }
.rte-btn { width: 30px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: 4px; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.rte-btn:hover { background: rgba(26,115,232,0.08); border-color: rgba(26,115,232,0.2); color: var(--primary); }
.rte-content { min-height: 100px; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0 0 6px 6px; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-primary); background: var(--input-bg); }
.rte-content:focus { border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26,115,232,0.1); }

/* Tag select */
.tag-item { padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--tag-border); background: var(--tag-bg); color: var(--text-secondary); transition: all .15s; display: inline-block; }
.tag-item:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary); }
.tag-item.selected { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-color: var(--primary); }
.tag-add-input { padding: 4px 8px; border: 1px solid var(--input-border); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; width: 90px; outline: none; background: var(--input-bg); color: var(--text-primary); }
.tag-add-input:focus { border-color: var(--primary); }
.tag-add-btn { padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
.tag-add-btn:hover { opacity: .85; }

/* Risk level radio */
.risk-level-radio { display: inline-flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 4px; }
.risk-level-radio label { padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; border: 2px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px; transition: all .15s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; background: var(--tag-bg); color: var(--text-secondary); }
.risk-level-radio label:hover { border-color: var(--primary); }
.risk-level-radio label.active-red { background: rgba(217,48,37,0.12); border-color: var(--dot-red); color: var(--dot-red); font-weight: 600; }
.risk-level-radio label.active-orange { background: rgba(227,116,0,0.12); border-color: var(--dot-orange); color: var(--dot-orange); font-weight: 600; }
.risk-level-radio label.active-yellow { background: rgba(249,171,0,0.12); border-color: var(--dot-yellow); color: #c68400; font-weight: 600; }
:root[data-theme="dark"] .risk-level-radio label.active-yellow { color: var(--dot-yellow); }
.risk-level-radio label.active-blue { background: rgba(26,115,232,0.12); border-color: var(--dot-blue); color: var(--dot-blue); font-weight: 600; }

/* Tri-switch */
.tri-switch { display: inline-flex; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.tri-switch label { padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; background: var(--tag-bg); transition: all .15s; color: var(--text-secondary); }
.tri-switch label:hover { background: var(--bg-hover); }
.tri-switch input:checked + .ts-on { background: rgba(30,142,62,0.15); color: var(--success); font-weight: 600; }
.tri-switch input:checked + .ts-pilot { background: rgba(227,116,0,0.12); color: var(--warning); font-weight: 600; }
.tri-switch input:checked + .ts-off { background: var(--bg-hover); color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 600; }

/* Measure tag */
.measure-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; padding: 4px 12px; background: rgba(26,115,232,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(26,115,232,0.2); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--primary); }
.measure-tag .remove { cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 16px; margin-left: 2px; }
.measure-tag .remove:hover { color: var(--danger); }

/* Measure select modal */
.select-measure-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
.select-measure-table th { padding: 10px 12px; text-align: left; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--header-bg); white-space: nowrap; }
.select-measure-table td { padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); vertical-align: top; }
.select-measure-table tr:hover td { background: var(--tree-row-hover); }
.select-measure-table td:first-child { text-align: center; width: 40px; }
.select-measure-table input[type="checkbox"] { width: 16px; height: 16px; cursor: pointer; accent-color: var(--primary); }
.smt-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 13px; }
.smt-desc { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 11px; margin-top: 2px; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; }
.smt-risk { padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; }
.smt-risk.red { background: rgba(217,48,37,0.12); color: var(--dot-red); }
.smt-risk.orange { background: rgba(227,116,0,0.12); color: var(--dot-orange); }
.smt-risk.yellow { background: rgba(249,171,0,0.12); color: var(--dot-yellow); }
.smt-risk.blue { background: rgba(26,115,232,0.12); color: var(--dot-blue); }
.select-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--header-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 13px; }
.select-bar .sel-count { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Filter Toolbar -->
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:12px">
    <div class="card-body" style="padding:12px 16px">
        <div class="filter-bar" style="margin-bottom:0">
            <input class="filter-input" placeholder="🔍 搜索风险条目..." style="flex:1;min-width:180px">
            <select class="filter-select">
                <option>全部风险主项</option>
                <option>建筑结构信息</option>
                <option>建筑基本信息</option>
            </select>
            <select class="filter-select">
                <option>全部风险等级</option>
                <option>重大风险（红）</option>
                <option>较大风险（橙）</option>
                <option>一般风险（黄）</option>
                <option>低风险（蓝）</option>
            </select>
            <button class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-search"></i> 查询</button>
            <button class="btn btn-outline">重置</button>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="openModal('modal-new-item')"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i> 新增条目</button>
            <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="openModal('modal-import-template')"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-import"></i> 批量导入</button>
            <button class="btn btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-export"></i> 导出</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Tree Table Card -->
<div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check" style="color:var(--primary)"></i> 农村自建房风险清单构建</div>
        <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary)">共2个主项 · 24个条目</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tree-table-header">
        <span>风险主项</span>
        <span>分项</span>
        <span>分项内容</span>
        <span style="text-align:center">风险标识</span>
        <span style="text-align:center">操作</span>
    </div>
    <div style="max-height:calc(100vh - 360px);overflow-y:auto">
        <!-- 建筑结构信息 -->
        <div class="tree-group-header" onclick="toggleTreeGroup(this)">
            <span style="flex:1"><span class="toggle-arrow">▼</span> 建筑结构信息</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tree-children">
            <div class="tree-row">
                <span>建筑结构信息</span><span>地基基础</span>
                <span class="cell-content">地基基础局部或整体塌陷；上部结构不均匀沉降裂缝严重，且继续发展尚未稳定，或已出现明显倾斜。</span>
                <span style="text-align:center"><span class="risk-dot red"></span></span>
                <span class="cell-actions" style="text-align:center">
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-view-item')">查看</a>
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-edit-item')">编辑</a>
                    <a class="del" onclick="openModal('modal-delete-confirm')">删除</a>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="tree-row">
                <span>建筑结构信息</span><span>地基基础</span>
                <span class="cell-content">地基基础出现少量损坏，有较明显的不均匀沉降，上部结构出现明显不均匀沉降裂缝，或外露基础明显腐蚀、酥碱、松散和剥落。</span>
                <span style="text-align:center"><span class="risk-dot orange"></span></span>
                <span class="cell-actions" style="text-align:center">
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-view-item')">查看</a>
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-edit-item')">编辑</a>
                    <a class="del" onclick="openModal('modal-delete-confirm')">删除</a>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="tree-row">
                <span>建筑结构信息</span><span>地基基础</span>
                <span class="cell-content">地基基础保持稳定，无明显不均匀沉降；上部结构有轻微不均匀沉降裂缝，外露基础基本完好。</span>
                <span style="text-align:center"><span class="risk-dot yellow"></span></span>
                <span class="cell-actions" style="text-align:center">
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-view-item')">查看</a>
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-edit-item')">编辑</a>
                    <a class="del" onclick="openModal('modal-delete-confirm')">删除</a>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="tree-row">
                <span>建筑结构信息</span><span>地基基础</span>
                <span class="cell-content">地基基础保持稳定，无明显不均匀沉降；上部结构无不均匀沉降裂缝和倾斜，外露基础完好。</span>
                <span style="text-align:center"><span class="risk-dot blue"></span></span>
                <span class="cell-actions" style="text-align:center">
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-view-item')">查看</a>
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-edit-item')">编辑</a>
                    <a class="del" onclick="openModal('modal-delete-confirm')">删除</a>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="tree-row">
                <span>建筑结构信息</span><span>墙体</span>
                <span class="cell-content">承重墙体有明显歪闪、局部酥碎或倒塌；墙角处和纵、横墙交接处普遍松动和开裂。</span>
                <span style="text-align:center"><span class="risk-dot red"></span></span>
                <span class="cell-actions" style="text-align:center">
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-view-item')">查看</a>
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-edit-item')">编辑</a>
                    <a class="del" onclick="openModal('modal-delete-confirm')">删除</a>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="tree-row">
                <span>建筑结构信息</span><span>墙体</span>
                <span class="cell-content">承重墙体多数受力裂缝，部分承重墙体明显位移和歪闪；部分山墙转角处和纵、横墙交接处有明显松动、脱闪现象。</span>
                <span style="text-align:center"><span class="risk-dot orange"></span></span>
                <span class="cell-actions" style="text-align:center">
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-view-item')">查看</a>
                    <a onclick="openModal('modal-edit-item')">编辑</a>
                    <a class="del" onclick="openModal('modal-delete-confirm')">删除</a>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="tree-row">
                <span>建筑结构信息</span><span>墙体</span>
                <span class="cell-content">承重墙体有少量受力裂缝和变形；墙体转角处和纵、横墙交接处无松动、脱闪现象。</span>
